Usage: KEYS
  Cursor left/right moves cursor in input line left and right
  Cursor up/down is for next/previous command
  PageUp or Alt-P scrolls backward
  PageDown or Alt-N scrolls forward
  Control-B toggles bold on/off
  Control-F shows netsplit information
  Control-K ban kicks last user to join from current channel
  Control-N accepts chat connection from last user to offer it
  Control-R inserts nick that last triggered auto reply
  Control-T is nick completion
  Control-V toggles reverse on/off
  Control-X switches channels
  Control-_ toggles underline on/off
  F1 this help
  F2 will join last channel you have been invited to
  
